{
  "stem": "20609.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they divided us into three groups, 50 apiece.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They put us in three cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And believe it or not, 50 was crowded because I-- recently, I went the museum in Washington.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went into one of those cars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, I can't believe 50 people spent four nights-- you know, four nights in a place like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Tell me about the car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a cattle car and it had a bucket in the back there and no-- no water, no nothing, just-- so we were loaded on and then the train took off, you know.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't much of a fast train, but I know we went-- we-- we could see we were going south, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We weren't going to any place-- so we went over the Danish border, which was not really a border at that time, it was strictly manned by a-- German people because they still didn't let German people into Denmark.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't want anybody to go to Denmark and buy-- smuggle things in, you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Know so there was a border there, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- and it was-- one side was German, the other side was a Danish office-- Danish customs officer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we went through that and all of a sudden, we're in Germany, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I know we passed in the outskirts of Hamburg and we were going south, kept on going south.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then many times, we pulled over and they don't open the goddamn thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the second-- we were two days already and two nights when we got out, finally opened the door, emptied the buckets, right, and get yourself some water.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't have a-- we didn't have a place to put water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had rubber boots, right.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
